rives a lot but never tired from driving, I offer him that I am ready for drive if he tired but he refused my offer & drive himself. Before hunt MR AZAM tell us \n\n               [b]O  SIR G   PARESHAAN  NAHI  HONA  KHULL  K  SHIKAAR  KARO[/b]\n\nHis offer give us extra sharpness in our eyes for hunt thank you so much azam \n\n                                              THANKS EVERYBODY \n                                                                          MAY YOU ALL LIVE LONG!', ''),
